    "body": "If the fix is `rpc-http-host=[\"0.0.0.0\"]` then I don't think that there is anything that Besu can do.  Besu will only be listening to 127.0.0.1 and the operating system will not forward any packets to besu.\r\n\r\nChanging the default `rpc-http-host` to anything but `127.0.0.1` is not an option because of our secure by default policy on network ports.  ",
